  "text": "The following three-step algorithm generates the monodromy matrix and hence the solution of the exclusion problem when there are two infected states (and at least 1 host type) and control u is constant [CITATION_1] [3] Adjust control u so that the dominant eigenvalue of matrix M equals 1. This is the value of u that gives zero growth over a cycle and hence exclusion.",
